expression: normalized
---
Validate eval configuration and files

Usage: fastskill eval validate [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -a, --agent <AGENT>    Target runtime(s) for this operation; repeatable (mutually exclusive with --all)
      --all              Target all runtimes discovered by aikit (mutually exclusive with --agent)
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format: table, json, grid, xml
      --json             Shorthand for --format json
  -h, --help             Print help

Examples:
  fastskill eval validate
  fastskill eval validate --agent codex
  fastskill eval validate --agent codex --agent claude
  fastskill eval validate --all
